WHAT? HOW COULD YOU JUST LEAVE IN THE MIDDLE OF THIS!?!?!?! ARGH!!!!!

    Nighteyes moved her head to the right, and felt a quick sarp pain as the 
shot hit the tree. Thank goodness fro her agility. She got up and began to 
sprint to cover, when Aerostreak slammed in to her.
    "Alright, come on, I think we can even the odds now." She said, and both 
crept behinde a large fallen Red Wood. "Theres a strange bot here too, I dont 
have a clue who she is though."
    Aerostreak aimed for Dollen, Nighteyes aimed for Drillbit, and both fired.

    Akron aimed her riffle at Dollen, and fired a threesome of energon 
blasts. She cursed as he kept moving, but then she sw Darkmouse. She cocked 
the riffle in her direction and blasted.
(Sorry Yan if I keep taking crappy shots at you while your not here, I know 
how fustrating that is.)

    Marine, Pheniox, and Jackle arrived at the Ice Caves. badly damaged, Hell 
Beast barely reconized them. "Get to the CR chambers. In the meantime 
Tarantulas and Tankkor go and help Nighteyes and Aerostreak. His signiture is 
in combat with Killfests group according the the map. Hussle!" He said, and 
coughed once more with the weakening virus.
